Analytical SQL: Replaces complex GROUP BY + JOIN logic
Partition + Order: Groups by key, ranks by freshness
Performance: Single-pass operation (efficient)
5. Data Quality Framework
Validation Metrics: Automated quality scoring
Reconciliation: Cross-layer consistency checks
Fail-Fast: Catches issues before Gold layer
